				<td colspan="2"><span>Bard, SK, Druid Trio.
<br />

<br />
Sk tags a Gaurd with snare dot.  Lets mob slmost reach him, then FD.  Others go back to the spawn, snared makes it halfway.  Bard tags with HoS, and brings it back.  Repeat for two remaining Guards.  Once Guards are handled, lull Excavators, and tag tarn.  Kill him.  If you get a spider add, charm it and use for extra DPS.
<br />

<br />
If you prefer, mez split the guards using fade, but you have to get a little more distance first, so the mobs don't reaggro when they pass by the Mezed Guard.
<br />

<br />
Rappa</span></td>
